divs: sighting detailsi had taken my dog out around 8:00pm and while he was in the back yard i had looked up and noticed the big dipper. i was facing south\ east and saw what i thought at first was a star,because that was the shape and color, but it was moving in an easterly direction and like a wobbly line. not side to side, but wobbly and going pretty quick. now just prior to and after, i did see planes in the sky, with there different colored blinking lights. that is why i knew this was not an airplane or a helicopter. there was no noise. it moved toward the east until i could no longer see it. like i stated, when i first saw this i said " no friggin way" " that's no star" i felt excited a little because like i said earlier, i saw planes in the sky then this object, and this was no plane.
Summary: Walking dog in backyard looked up and saw an object moving wobbly
